{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/tech/zykt-helper/devlog-1/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"mem 的小站"}},"post":{"id":"2e20d04b-5657-57e9-9eb6-4aa4d2411d9d","excerpt":"作为现代的大学生，自然是非常喜欢使用智云课堂。 However…","html":"<p>作为现代的大学生，自然是非常喜欢使用智云课堂。</p>\n<p>However，作为，多少有点不好用的地方。</p>\n<p>本着“求人不如求己”的原则，在使用了智云课堂一个学期之后，我决定还是自己上手开发一个智云课堂的辅助脚本。</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-08ef46335aad7322\" style=\"position: relative;\">技术选型<a href=\"#anchor-08ef46335aad7322\" aria-label=\"anchor 08ef46335aad7322 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>考虑到智云课堂的使用场景，这款辅助脚本并不需要特别“轻量”，而应该把该做的功能都做了，同时还有较高的可维护性（方便传宗接代给之后的小朋友维护）。</p>\n<p>思量一番后还是考虑选用之前试过的 webpack 方案。我的博客曾经有一篇文章怎么用 webpack 配合 TamperMonkey 开发用户脚本，但后来觉得写的过于垃圾就删掉了==</p>\n<p>首先按照一般方式创建一个 webpack 项目，npm 装包的过程就省略了，请自行参考我的 package.json。</p>\n<p>填入 webpack 配置如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ./webpack.config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">entry</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/index.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">output</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">filename</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'bundle.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">module</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">rules</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">test</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\.js$</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">use</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'babel-loader'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">test</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\.css$</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">use</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'style-loader'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'css-loader'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-08ef46335aad7322\">技术选型</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"智云课堂辅助脚本开发日志（一）：启动","date":null,"description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/tech/zykt-helper/devlog-1/","isDoc":null,"category":"[]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"2e20d04b-5657-57e9-9eb6-4aa4d2411d9d","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":""}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}